    title: "Affordable Sober Living in South Florida: What You Can Expect at Every Price Point",
    excerpt:
      "South Florida has some of the best — and worst — sober living options in the country. Here's how to find affordable recovery housing without sacrificing the quality and structure that actually works.",
    date: "2026-03-30",
